# AI tooling — intentionally tracked
# OpenSpec change artifacts (proposal/design/specs/tasks) and Claude skills +
# slash commands are intentionally committed so they survive across machines
# and sessions. The `!` rules below are defensive: if a broader ignore pattern
# is added later, these paths remain tracked.
!/openspec/
!/.claude/skills/
!/.claude/commands/
